# This public repo carries ONLY the public-facing overview (README.md) and the presentation
# (docs/index.html). The actual Google Apps Script application - server code (.gs), HTML
# templates, appsscript.json, security model, validation rules, sheet structure - stays inside
# Google Apps Script only, managed locally via clasp, and is deliberately never committed here.
# This is an allowlist, not a denylist: everything is ignored by default, and only the files
# explicitly un-ignored below will ever be tracked. If you add a new file that should be public,
# add a matching "!" line for it - don't loosen the leading "*".
*

!.gitignore
!README.md
!docs/
!docs/index.html
